= Workspace Hand

This is a whiteboard hand scene. It gives the project a ready-made card surface:
one deck lane for action cards and one pinned advisor lane.

In a larger mod, this can become the place where monthly actions, party work,
advisors, circles, or other repeatable systems live.

- @demo_action_deck: Draw from the starter deck
- #demo_advisor: Review starter advisor
- @root: Back to start
